Latest info:

To build IOS code, if it is from a new view, need to build dependencies:

cd /vob/ios/sys
make -j8 dependencies

Then build the IOS image

cd /vob/ios/sys/obj-ppc-galaxy
make -j8 REBUILD_ALL=1

If you also want to include debugging info, then add the option
    GALAXY_IOS_DEVELOPMENT=1

To specify the suffix of the image:
make -j8 BIN_SUFFIX=".whatever" cat4000-i5su3-mz

